data.description: Welcome to this turnkey 2-story home in the Waukee Northwest school district near Grant Ragan elementary, conveniently located off Alice's Rd, near HyVee and a new neighborhood park right around the corner! You get so much more in this better-than-new resale with all appliances included, 'Nest' doorbell, thermostat, and smoke alarms, fully fenced backyard, upgraded patio, AND all window coverings done for you! Great open concept plan with spacious kitchen and sink overlooking the backyard, granite countertops, tile backsplash, breakfast bar, pantry and stainless steel appliances that all stay! Convenient built-in locker with bench near both front and garage door. Head up the lighted stairway to all 4 bedrooms, including the primary suite with vaulted ceilings and ensuite bathroom with attached walk-in closet. Full hall bath complements the 3 additional bedrooms. Convenient 2nd level laundry room with washer and dryer on pedestals - included! Spread out in the finished lower level with a large great room, dry bar, & 3/4 bathroom. Don't wait, fall is a perfect time to get settled into your new home!
